author: COMSOL
description: A steel cylinder is pressed into an aluminum block. The cylinder is subjected to a uniform load along its top. The contact pressure distribution and contact length computed using the penalty method, both augmented Lagrangian methods, and the Nitsche method are compared with the analytical solution.
